{"tid":1602134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲多市遊行集會聲援港人爭取五大訴求","createTime":"2019-09-29T10:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:52:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"606b0fcc34ceab517096c8944603595aacfe9f3e","tid":1602134,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"全球多個城市今日舉行反極權遊行集會活動，澳洲7個城市響應，其中悉尼及布里斯本分別有800人及逾百參加遊行。<br />\n<br />\n悉尼有800人參加遊行，支持港人爭取五大訴求。參與遊行的人士首先在新南威爾士州立圖書館集會，遊行至終點市中心內遊客區的維多尼亞女王大廈，沿途叫口號要光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國倫敦周末亦有反極權遊行，以及支持爭取五大訴求。部分遊行人士抵達唐人街時，一名在場男子手持五星旗走入遊行人士當中，受到包圍及叫罵。該名男子其後離開，但部分人緊隨，一直向他叫罵。<br />\n<br />\n全球60多個城市今日料將有反極權遊行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2262638/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2262638%2F&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=31bea469\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2262638/</a>"},{"pid":"dfa4e08b3fe373fb2bfe75bb175403c8be755f1c","tid":1602134,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"感謝澳洲人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj